ЁЯЪА Effortlessly export Booking hotel reviews from detail page to XLS/CSV file.

ЁЯФз How it Works:
1я╕ПтГг Open an Booking hotel detail page.
2я╕ПтГг Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3я╕ПтГг Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

ЁЯФе Key Features:
1я╕ПтГг Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2я╕ПтГг Export on multiple hotel detail pages simultaneous.
3я╕ПтГг Export reviews for current item to a xls/csv file, data include: Hotel Name, User Name, Country, Room Info, Stay Date, Traveller Type, Badge, Review Date, Review Title, Score, Like Review, Dislike Review, Helpfull, Hotel URL.

ЁЯОп Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.
